        {
            "title": "UBS在蘋果財報前上調目標價,看好iPhone市佔率提升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/64M9sATm19uqdzdtp4hFYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7B05U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - UBS已將蘋果目標價從每股280美元上調至287美元,這是在該公司季度財報發布前做出的調整,理由是記憶體價格上漲正在擠壓Android競爭對手,從而推動iPhone市場份額增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"使用InvestingPro專業工具即時追蹤每一次分析師升級、降級和目標價變動\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:使用InvestingPro專業工具即時追蹤每一次分析師升級、降級和目標價變動;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/landing-page?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">使用InvestingPro專業工具即時追蹤每一次分析師升級、降級和目標價變動</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行維持對<span><span><span><span>蘋果</span></span></span></span>的中性評級,表示預計3月季度業績將略微超出預期,預測營收為1,090億美元,而市場共識為1,093億美元,小幅上行空間主要由iPhone和Mac需求推動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c5f50e0f-94fa-32b8-8b0b-2b2629609985-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">UBS預測該季度iPhone營收為562億美元,供應鏈檢查和銷售數據顯示將有小幅超出表現。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在服務業務方面,UBS預計不會超出其約14%的營收增長預測,指出「支付業務的強勁表現被App Store的溫和增長所抵消」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司預測合併毛利率為48.5%,稀釋每股收益將比其1.94美元的預估高出幾美分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱更重要的修正涉及6月季度展望。UBS將6月營收預測上調約4%至1,020億美元,意味著8.5%的年增長率,因為「記憶體驅動的市佔率增長」促使該銀行將iPhone出貨量預測從4,650萬部上調至5,030萬部。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">UBS認為蘋果正在包括中國和歐洲在內的關鍵市場從Android設備手中奪取市場份額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在毛利率方面,UBS指出較高的記憶體成本將對產品毛利率造成環比和年比壓力,預計6月毛利率區間為47%至48%。該銀行將6月季度每股收益預估上調約7%至1.70美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ubs%E5%9C%A8%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B9-%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BDiphone%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%94%E7%8E%87%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87-142150854.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 22:47:21",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美伊僵局持續,歐洲天然氣價格波動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週二歐洲<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"天然氣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:天然氣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/天然氣\">天然氣</a>價格表現平淡,投資者正在評估美國與伊朗談判明顯陷入僵局的局面,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>實際上仍處於關閉狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間上午8:42(格林威治標準時間12:43),荷蘭TTF樞紐基準近月合約小幅上漲0.1%,至每兆瓦時44.71歐元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">媒體報導指出,美國總統川普對伊朗提出的提議並不滿意,該提議將結束雙方長達兩個月的衝突並重新開放霍爾木茲海峽,但將有關德黑蘭核野心的討論推遲到稍後階段。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cf3e8964-d68c-3707-a72d-97393f3d07c0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普經常表示,消除伊朗的核能力,特別是其獲得核武器的能力,一直是2月底發動的美以聯合攻擊的推動力。據路透社援引一位了解此事的美國官員報導,正因如此,川普對該提議感到不滿。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週末期間,美國與伊朗和平談判重啟的希望受挫,川普取消派遣談判代表前往巴基斯坦進行新一輪會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在所有外交角力之中,霍爾木茲海峽幾乎仍對航運交通關閉。這條位於伊朗南部海岸的狹窄水道是一個關鍵咽喉要道,全球約五分之一的液化天然氣通過此處,該水道已被實際封鎖數週,推動天然氣價格飆升至戰前水平以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外,西北歐洲的氣溫預計將上升至本週末,然後逐漸降溫。據路透社援引歐洲天然氣基礎設施組織數據報導,歐盟天然氣儲存設施最近的填充率為31.75%,而一年前為38.42%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>(路透社提供報導)</em></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95-140503407.html",
